<div class="parallax" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path 'parallax_bg.jpg' %>)">
  <div class="banner-content animated fadeInUp">
    <div class="banner-text">
      <h1>Become a petsitter!</h1>
      <p>
        Do you want to take care of a cute dog? <br> How about playing for a few hours with a cat?
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-wrapper">
      <div class="banner-cta">
        <%= link_to "Find a pet!", pets_path %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="about-wrapper">
  <div class="about-left">
    <%= image_tag(asset_path 'pets_group.png') %>
    <div class="circle"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-right">
    <h2>Why Pettoren?</h2>
    <div class="services-wrapper">
      <div class="service">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
            <%= image_tag(asset_path 'nearby.png') %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text">
          <h4>Find nearby pets</h4>
          <p>Find pets using search bar, filters or distace sliders. You will find a new friend for sure!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
            <%= image_tag(asset_path 'pet.png') %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text">
          <h4>Choose the pet</h4>
          <p>Learn more about the pet and it's availability. Check out all the cute photos too!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
      <div class="icon-wrapper">
        <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
          <%= image_tag(asset_path 'booking.png') %>
        </div>
      </div>
        <div class="text">
          <h4>Book your pet</h4>
          <p>Book the pet you like according to your schedule. Don't worry, you will find an open day.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="service">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <div class="icon d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
            <%= image_tag(asset_path 'dashboard-interface.png') %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text">
          <h4>Manage booking</h4>
          <p>Check the status of your booking in your dashboard. Is your booking still pending?</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="statistics-wrapper d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
  <div class="statistics">
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number"> <span id="pet-count" data-count="<%= Pet.count %>"></span></div>
      <div class="stat-text">Pets</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <% pics_number = 0 %>
      <% Pet.all.each do |pet| %>
      <% pics_number += pet.pet_pics.count %>
      <% end %>
      <div class="stat-number"><span id="pic-count" data-count=" <%= pics_number %> "></span></div>
      <div class="stat-text">Pets pictures</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <div class="stat-number"><span id="user-count" data-count="<%= User.count %>"></span></div>
      <div class="stat-text">Users</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="parallax-reviews" style="background-image: url(<%= asset_path 'parallax_reviews.jpg' %>)">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="review-section">
      <div class="review-title">
        <h2>Happy Petsitters</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-wrapper">
        <div class="carousel">
          <div class="owl-carousel owl-theme">
            <div class="item" id="item-review">
              <div class="review-wrapper">
                <p>I found a cute buddy thanks to Pettoren. I'm playing with him every Saturday!</p>
                <div class="review-user">
                  <img src="" alt="avatar">
                  <div class="name"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item" id="item-review">
              <div class="review-wrapper">
                <p>My apartment is not alowing pets. Then I've discovered this website. I can find a pet to rent wiht just a few clicks.</p>
                <div class="review-user">
                  <img src="" alt="avatar">
                  <div class="name"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item" id="item-review">
              <div class="review-wrapper">
                <p>I always wanted to have an animal, but I can't afford to have one. I was looking for a solution to my problem and found Pettoren.</p>
                <div class="review-user">
                  <img src="" alt="avatar">
                  <div class="name"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item" id="item-review">
              <div class="review-wrapper">
                <p>As an owner of a long cat T-shirt I wanted to find a real cat to play with. Now I can!</p>
                <div class="review-user">
                  <img src="" alt="avatar">
                  <div class="name"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item" id="item-review">
              <div class="review-wrapper">
                <p>I used to have a lot of pets, but since I moved to Japan I can't even own a hamster. With pettoren I can play with lots a of pets.</p>
                <div class="review-user">
                  <img src="" alt="avatar">
                  <div class="name"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container gallery">
  <h2>Pets gallery</h2>
  <div class="pets-all-list">
      <% @pets.each do |pet| %>
        <% if pet.pet_pics.attached? %>
          <%= link_to pet_path(pet[:id]) do %>
            <div class="pet-card gallery" data-species="<%= pet.species %>" style="background-position: center;background-size: cover;background-image: url('<%= cl_image_path pet.pet_pics.first.key%>')">
              <div class="pet-info-wrapper gallery">
                <div class="pet-info gallery">
                  <h4><%= pet.name %></h4>
                  <p><%= pet.breed %></p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
</div>

